{
  "stem": "6989.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know, people were killing Jews and groups.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Poles.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, I believe we went to Czechoslovakia, as Greek-- as Greeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember crossing the border and not being allowed to talk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Illegally, illegally.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were supposed to be Greeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because apparently Greeks were allowed to go, and Jews were not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you know, you live your whole life in fear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all I remember is fear, fear, fear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe they must have been.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this was organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't just us alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like, a whole caravan of people--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--crossing, you know, into Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Czechoslovakia, we stayed a very short time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we came to the DP camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jenny ?] and [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rubin ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Greenberg. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If they were, it was distant-- I mean, I-- I never really asked them what they--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had one son.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was younger, 3 and 1/2 years younger, I think, than I.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, I think they really-- originally she came to see the-- they had property and things like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think she came to see her house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And things like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then she found out that I was--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--alone.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just one person.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were very good with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think like, I wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, they were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I-- I guess I missed Lena, or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That I just wasn't the same person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, this was much, much later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if it was in Germany or in the United States, that somebody came and said that they were hidden in the bunker.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They ran out of food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, as you can see in the picture, was a heavy woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
